<p>by.</p>
<p>10th. August<br/>Shower early but cleared off later. Bath parade &amp; clean clothes later. Mail rec'd.</p>
<p>11th. Friday<br/>Warned off at Bkfast time to report to Bgde Hqrs. for Course of bayonet instructions for one week.</p>
<p>Tommy Sgt Major of the Coldstream Guards very good indeed, got very stiff with exercises &amp; play he gave us.</p>
<p>12th. Saturday<br/>Continued instruction knocked off about 3pm till Monday. Concert evening.</p>
